Run with:

```
bundle install
bundle exec puma
```

Then test with:

```
curl -X GET -H "X-Forwaded-Host: host1" -H "X-Forwarded-Host: host2" -H "X-Forwarded-Host: host3" http://localhost:9292
curl -X GET -H "X-Forwaded-Host: host1" -H "X-Forwarded-Host: host2" http://localhost:9292
curl -X GET -H "X-Forwaded-Host: host1" http://localhost:9292
```


Change Gemfile for good and bad revision of rack
